- represents HAS-A relationship
- relation between two separate classes
- a class have an entity ref
- loosely coupled

association - relation between two separate classes which establishes thro their objects
Two forms of association
1. Composition - strong bonding
2. Aggregation - weak bonding

class Vehicle{

}
class Car extends Vehicle{
    Engine engine = new Engine();
    MPlayer mPlayer = new MPlayer();
}
class Engine{ //Composition

}
class MPlayer{ //Aggregation
}